lead_paragraph: Southwest Airlines agreed to make room temporarily for Delta Air Lines at its gates at Dallas Love Field Airport while the carriers await a long-term resolution of their dispute in court.

headline.main: Southwest Agrees to Share With Delta at a Dallas Airport
